snippet.title: Medieval II: Total War Kingdoms - Britannia Campaign Trailer
snippet.description:
For more video game shenanigans head over to my channel! http://www.youtube.com/user/anders1211/

This is the trailer for the expansion pack of medieval 2: total war, here u can see details about the britania campaign and the factions belonging to it.
